src:
Da li će doći u Beograd: As Totenhema ne igra protiv Evertona
03 Nov 2019, 15:27 by Milos
Totenhem od 17.30 časova gostuje Evertonu u Liverpulu u okviru 11. kola Premijer lige.
Strateg „pevaca“ Mauricio Poketino na ovom susretu neće moći da računa na prvu zvezdu tima Harija Kejna, koji je ostao u Londonu.
Mediji na Ostrvu pišu, kako je kapiten reprezentacije Engleske bolestan i da postoji mogućnost da sjajni napadač propusti meč sa Crvenom zvezdom u Ligi šampiona. Podsetimo duel u Beogradu se igra, u sredu, 6. novembra od 21 čas.

POVEZANE OBJAVE
text:
Will he come to Belgrade: As Tottenham does not play against Everton
03 Nov 2019, 15:27 by Milos
Tottenham host Everton in Liverpool as part of the 11th round of the Premier League.
Singer strategist Mauricio Poketino will not be able to count on the first star of team Harry Kane to stay in London at this meeting.
The island's media writes that the captain of the England national team is ill and there is a possibility that the striker will miss the match with the Red Star in the Champions League. Recall a duel in Belgrade is played on Wednesday, November 6 from 9 pm.
